com.thetransactioncompany.cors
Class Origin

java.lang.Object
  com.thetransactioncompany.cors.Origin

public class Origin
extends java.lang.Object

Represents a resource request origin, as defined in IETF's draft-abarth-origin-07. Supported protocols are http, https and file.

Examples: 

         http://www.example.com
         https://sso.example.com:8080
         http://192.168.0.1
         file:///data/file.html
         null

Version:
1.3.2 (2010-09-24)
Author:
Vladimir Dzhuvinov
